title: Amy's Prank Call About Feeding Dog Treats To Her Kids + Clay Walker Performs His Biggest 90’s Hits + Good Parent, Bad Parent: Eddie Threw His 7-Year Old Into The Water
itunes:title: Amy's Prank Call About Feeding Dog Treats To Her Kids + Clay Walker Performs His Biggest 90’s Hits + Good Parent, Bad Parent: Eddie Threw His 7-Year Old Into The Water
description:
Amy does her first prank call in 10 years. She calls to ask why her kids are having trouble chewing the "milk" bone cookies she bought from their store. Clay Walker stops by and performs his biggest 90’s hits. Plus, Eddie threw his son into the water while out on the boat so we debate whether it makes him a good or bad parent!
